&lt;p>Only the basic functionality is given - use &lt;code>?function_name&lt;/code> for details on loading specific parts.
For reading CSV files, &lt;code>stringsAsFactors = FALSE&lt;/code> will load as a character string, which can be helpful, albeit more expensive in memory.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3>CSV&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="csv">&lt;/span>
