&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Percentages in ggplot2</title><link>https://David-Manning.github.io/cheat_sheets/r/percentages_in_ggplot2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://David-Manning.github.io/cheat_sheets/r/percentages_in_ggplot2/</guid><description>
&lt;p>Use this syntax to format as percentages:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To go to 1 decimal place, use:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(accuracy = 0.1))&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(accuracy = 0.1))&lt;/code>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>